 ↞---------------|ABILITIES|---------------↠

  Gluttony:

    This Pokémon eats any held 
  Berry triggered by low HP when 
  it falls below 50% of its HP, 
  regardless of the Berry's usual 
  threshold.

  Overgrow:

    When this Pokémon has 1/3 or 
  less of its HP remaining, its 
  grass-type moves inflict 1.5× 
  as much regular damage.


